headline: CFOs On the Move: Week ending Dec. 19
summary: S&P Global names a Booz Allen exec as CFO of its planned mobility spinoff, Marathon Petroleum hires a new finance chief and Cardlytics will bring back its former CFO.

headline: Marathon Petroleum (MPC) Valuation Check After Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Marathon Petroleum (MPC) has been drifting lower over the past month, even as its long term track record still looks solid. That pullback is what makes the stock interesting right now.
